PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by the SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION and by TRANSGAS LIMITED of their statutory power to acquire a right-of-way on COWESSESS INDIAN RESERVE NO. 73 in Saskatchewan, for the purposes of an electrical power transmission system and a natural gas pipeline, and (b) granting each of them an easement for those purposes, in lieu thereof.
